---
layout: branded.hbs
subject: Customer Account Activation
---
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
    {% if customer.name %}
    <tr>
        <td class="content-block"><h1>Dear \{{ customer.name }},</h1></td>
    </tr>
    {% endif %}
    <tr>
        <td class="content-block"><h2>This is to confirm that your account for the shop \{{ shop.name }} is now active.</h2></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="content-block">The next time you shop at \{{ shop.name }}, you can save time at checkout by logging into your account. This will prefill your address information at the checkout.</td>
    </tr>
</table>
